data.title: “Every father should remember one day his son will follow his example, not his advice.” ― Charles F. Kettering This couldn’t be more true....
data.meta_description:
222 likes, 24 comments - trav_cole_ on July 2, 2024: "“Every father should remember one day his son will follow his example, not his advice.” ― Charles F. Kettering
This couldn’t be more true. I didn’t pick Brooklyns clothes out. He did. He saw them in a store and picked them out himself. Today, he asked to go on a run with me. I didn’t ask he asked me. 
Great reminder that our kids are watching our every move. I just pray they see more good than my bad ;)
